<p>Checking out source content</p><p>Lock the source content for your work package. 
  </p> 
	  
		<ul> 
		   
			  Content from a CMS must be
				linked to the work package. 
			  
		   
		 
		</ul><p> 
		   
			 <p>If your product does not use a
				CMS connection, then you must access your CMS directly to lock the content for
				editing. 
			 </p> 
		   
		</p>  
		<p> Through CORDAP, you can check out
		  source content linked to your assigned work package. 
		</p> 
	  
	  
		 
		  Find the desired work package in 
			 My Work or the 
			 Work Packages tab. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Expand the work package to show 
			 Source content. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Expand 
			 Source content. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click 
			 Check out beside each desired piece of
			 content. 
		   
		 
	  
	  
		<p> The CMS locks each selected piece
		  of content. 
		</p> 
	  
  